title: Google Launches Accelerator For Blockchain Companies
author: Maria Gracia Santillana Linares
description: Web3 companies accepted into the Google for Startups Cloud program will receive funding and technical support from over 10 digital businesses, including Coinbase.

title: Why The Unbanked In Europe Don’t Use Crypto For Daily Payments
author: Ifigenia Georgiou
description: “Oh, the unbanked are not using crypto!” Monique Morrow, co-founder of the Swiss nonprofit The Humanized Internet, told me in an interview.
